makes over 30% of their workforce dependent on goverment jobs.
__________________________________________________________

And so, we will keep looking for a viable and affordable earthbound
site for this vessel... Perhaps it will require nothing else than
"sovereignty" for this vessel to succeed, by which I mean either an
existing sponsor country (as mentioned by the originator of this
